## Hunting Dashboards

Create a dashboard combining multiple detections:

```spl
<dashboard>
  <label>MuddyWater APT Threat Hunt</label>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>Spearphishing Detection</title>
      <single>
        <search>
          <query>index=main sourcetype=WinEventLog:Security EventCode=1
          parent_process_name IN (winword.exe, excel.exe, powerpnt.exe)
          process_name IN (powershell.exe, cmd.exe, wscript.exe)
          | stats count</query>
        </search>
      </single>
    </panel>
    <panel>
      <title>Credential Dumping Events</title>
      <single>
        <search>
          <query>index=main sourcetype=WinEventLog:Security EventCode=1
          process_command_line="*sekurlsa::logonpasswords*"
          NOT process_command_line="*Picus*"
          | stats count</query>
        </search>
      </single>
    </panel>
  </row>
</dashboard>
```
